Package org.hibernate.validator.internal.constraintvalidators.bv.number.bound

package org.hibernate.validator.internal.constraintvalidators.bv.number.bound
Contains ConstraintValidator implementations for min and max constraints for numbers.
Author:
Marko Bekhta
